title: SanDisk microSD to SD Memory Card Adapter (MICROSD-ADAPTER)
description: Need to use your micro SD card in an SD card slot? This SanDisk micro SD to SD memory card adapter is designed for use in devices with a standard Secure Digital slot! It features a built-in write protection switch to keep your data safe! Order today! Features/Specifications: SanDisk micro SD to SD Memory Card Adapter General Features: micro SD to SD card adapter Built-in write protection switch For use in devices with a standard Secure Digital slot Unit Dimensions:1.25 x 0.9 x 0.1-inches (H x W x D, approximate) Package Includes: SanDisk micro SD to SD Memory Card Adapter Additional Information: Notes: micro SD card is for picture representational purposes only Product Requirements : micro SD memory card Device with a standard Secure Digital slot
